{"tid":1850854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家黎緊大大力咁懲罰AbouThai","createTime":"2020-01-29T18:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-29T18:11:03.000Z","uid":69525,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"194c783d6e56f7ef29d599b4a275015525e57314","tid":1850854,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:00:04.000Z","msg":"今日真係辛苦哂老細<br />\n明明責任唔應該係你到 應該係香港政府既責任<br />\n多謝老細同各分店員工既幫助同付出<br />\n<br />\n希望大家對同路人態度好啲<br />\n今日見到大量既人屌柒啲staff同醫護<br />\n醫療又屌柒啲員工留得少貨<br />\n雖然可能呢啲人係藍絲廢老 <br />\n但我都肯定少部分同路人都有份屌<br />\n<br />\n希望以後再有黃店比人屌既時間<br />\n大家身為同路人 幫一幫口 趕走啲藍絲廢老<br />\n唔好令到啲staff比人圍同難做<br />\n今日我果區無乜人幫口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後無咩想講<br />\n希望以後大家大大力懲罰AbouThai<br />\n老細賣口罩計埋運費人手時間 <br />\n應該都無賺甚至蝕比大家<br />\n大家拍硬檔 買佢地其他product 幫襯老細"},{"pid":"4e1cc48288c5574f57276d1f2adbe53545ff2905","tid":1850854,"uid":258731,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/308/5d9705d903228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F308%2F5d9705d903228.jpg&h=786cb045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港共正利用武漢肺炎進行第9步：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">種族清洗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n透過邊境不設防<br />\n高調宣揚非本地人士免費優先治療武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n蓄意引導大量染病支那人來港<br />\n摧毀香港已經長期超負荷的醫療系統，令香港人大規模感染<br />\n而無法隔離或治理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><br />\n中共打算將香港將變成武漢，市民無法睇醫生，橫屍街頭<br />\n意圖對香港人進行大屠殺</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港獨立 港中區隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n而家已經係獨立最佳時機，你，仲等緊啲咩<br />\n香港人，仲唔反佢老母？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9f4946687b0f9de9b30373ae1a9d6f58d970a6","tid":1850854,"uid":131933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:01:33.000Z","msg":"仲有程班長"},{"pid":"2a5edf243d0ccfa1b602eb0cf88917e84c3cc3b7","tid":1850854,"uid":321618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:01:54.000Z","msg":"真 呢個時候香港人更加要團結<br />\n<br />\n醫護手足 點可以因為一場本可以封關避免嘅病毒而賭上生命<br />\n我地仲未光復到香港啊..<br />\nbtw p牌求推一推... <img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥  借刀殺人<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850782</a>"},{"pid":"436e3f201af0403d21fe93380a5c96f2e2526e9b","tid":1850854,"uid":65556,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:09:27.000Z","msg":"推 記住阿布泰老闆就係活生生一個被政權剝削既香港人 因為沙田水貨客所以佢連海關都無得做 但偏偏就要幫香港政府執屎"},{"pid":"f3674c719a34066ef3c618c61b15886a4b67ccf4","tid":1850854,"uid":258370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}